description: Welcome to your city retreat at The Manor House Unit 2109, a move-in ready condo designed for modern urban living. This freshly updated home offers two spacious bedrooms with large walk-in closets and two sleek bathrooms featuring a double vanity, walk-in shower, and a Japanese-style soaking tub perfect for relaxing after a long day. The open living area includes hardwood floors, nine-foot ceilings, abundant natural light, and a stainless-steel and granite kitchen that overlooks the living space, making it ideal for entertaining or unwinding. Added conveniences include a private laundry room with washer and dryer, brand-new carpet in the bedrooms, two deeded parking spaces (#51 & #156)  in a secure garage, a 24-hour concierge for peace of mind, and even a dog walk for your furry friend. Located on a tree-lined street that feels like a neighborhood but sits just minutes from the Beltline, Bobby Jones Golf Course, shopping, and dining, this condo blends comfort, style, and city convenience between Buckhead and Midtown. Don’t miss your chance to experience true urban elegance—schedule your tour today to see this beautifully renovated and staged home!
